_sText:
Designed and mapped by Steezy

Notes

Revamped version of Italia.

Map features

  • Random gun cells
  • Different guns spawned every round
  • 7 breakable vents
  • 1 random teleport in cell
  • 1 secret teleport to skybox then to armoury

Activities

  • Dodge the Italian flag game
  • Battle Crates
  • Dodge the barrel game
  • 3 rooms of death
  • Bunny hop
  • Jump game
  • Disco Colours
  • Table game
  • Theatre
  • Trampoline
  • Football pitch
  • Club (5 songs)

Credits

Disco songs

  • I Bet You Look Good on the Dancefloor - Arctic Monkeys
  • Cage The Elephant - Trouble
  • Outkast - Ms. Jackson
  • Skepta - That's Not Me
  • The Strokes - Last Nite

Thank's to Ollie for testing way back when.
